high_descs: Turn right, move to the counter between the stove and toaster.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn left, move to the end of the counter, in front of the bin.
Slice the left apple in the bin into sections.
Turn right, move to the counter between the coffee maker and dishwasher.
Put the knife on the shelf, left of the bottle.
Turn left, move to the end of the counter, in front of the bin.
Pick up a apple section from the bin.
Turn right, move to the counter, in front of the microwave.
Put the apple section in the microwave, cook it, pick it back up.
Turn right, move to the counter between the coffee maker and dishwasher.
Put the apple section on the shelf, left of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked slice of apple onto the counter.

high_descs: Head to the sink then hang right and walk to the counter that is next to the stove on your left. The one that the toaster is on
Pick up the butter knife that is sitting on the counter
Turn around and cross the room then hang a right and walk to the trash can that is sitting to the right of the fridge.  It is in between the counter and the fridge
Slice the green apple that is sitting inside on the left
Turn to the right and walk to the sink, then turn left and face the counter top.
Place the knife on the back shelf of the countertop to the left of the vase
Turn left and walk to the trash can than is sandwiched in between the fridge and counter top on your right
Pick up a slice of the apple
Turn right and walk to the microwave that is sitting on the counter above the dishwasher
Open the microwave and place the apple inside on the right of the egg then close the door and turn it on. Then open the microwave and pick up the slice of apple and close the door
Turn to the right and walk to the sink and then turn left and face the counter
Place the slice of apple on the top shelf of the counter, to the left of the butter knife
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked apple on a counter

high_descs: Go to the right of the stove
Pick up the knife
Go to the bin right of the fridge
Cut the apple on the left
Go to the counter shelf near the coffeemaker
Put the knife down on the shelf
Go to the bin right of the fridge
Pick up an apple slice
Go to the microwave
Heat the apple slice
Go to the counter shelf near the coffeemaker
Put the apple slice next to the knife
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked apple slice and a knife on a shelf
